trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner class is a base class for deriving your own data source designer for a custom data source control derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl> class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner er en basisklasse for avledes dine egne datakilde designer for en egendefinert datakildekontroll avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl>

trans-unit.source: Other classes that derive from HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner are <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Det er andre klasser som er avledet fra HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The OnDataSourceChanged method notifies the designer of each control bound to the associated data source to refresh its control in the design host.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnDataSourceChanged varsler utformeren av hver kontrollen som er bundet til den tilknyttede datakilden til å oppdatere kontrollen i utformingen verten.

trans-unit.source: This method can be suppressed with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A> method, or by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> method with an argument of `false`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan undertrykkes med den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>metode, eller ved å ringe det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A>metode med et argument i `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>

trans-unit.target: Hever den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SchemaRefreshed"> </xref> -hendelse når skjemaet for datakilden er endret og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>egenskapsverdi <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>

trans-unit.source: This method notifies the designers of each control bound to the associated data source that the fields in the schema have changed.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden varsler utviklere for hver kontrollen som er bundet til tilknyttet datakilden som felt i skjemaet er endret.

trans-unit.source: This method can be suppressed with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A> method, or by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> method with an argument of `true`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan undertrykkes med den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>metode, eller ved å ringe det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A>metode med et argument i `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>
